Singer 9ice and his wife Sunkanmi have welcomed new child. The Gongo aso crooner made the announcement via his Instagram page. He posted a lovely photo shoot of his wife heavily pregnant with the caption: “My baby just delivered a baby” His wife also shared picture on her page and wrote: “God has been beyond showing out in my life since the beginning of 2021.   Adekunle Gold releases much anticipated album     How to know if you’re a side chick/ guy, by Morey Faith     Wizkid’s song inspired me to do music – Portable   - Advertisement - “I am grateful to him I can’t even begin to put it into words. Everything isnt always sinshine when God blesses you. “You really do have to be careful and be ready for all the residues that comes with it. And in it you believe he would never give you more than you can bear. I am super duper thankful. “Thank you Lord for this new addition to our family. Just know baby Myla that you wished for, longed for, prayed for, and will be forever loved” 9ice and Olasunkanmi had been friends for a decade before they got married on December 24, 2019.